data.description: Conveniently located home now on the market and can be yours. Freshly painted interior with 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms with a large flex room on the main floor. Great sized kitchen that overlooks the dining area and family room. Great floor plan that has all bedrooms on the second floor. Master en-suite has views with no rear neighbors. Dual vanity with separate tub and shower. Enjoy a great walk-in closet with plenty of storage located throughout. Additional bedrooms are good sized and private from the entertaining areas below. Split 3 car garage (one car garage was use as a movie room by previous owner but not included in the square footage). Very private and low maintenance yard with synthetic grass. Do not miss this opportunity!
